Discover a whole new world of artistic freedom here at @Azulik Uh May. ✨ Come find us in the creative crevices of the Uh May residence and unravel the secrets of this modern paradise.

Treat your senses to the boundless tastes of @junglecuisine.azulik —a sustainable, high-end culinary experience that brings you back to the welcoming arms of Mother Nature.🍃

What are you waiting for? Book that next flight out and join us on this unforgettable adventure! 
📍 @AZULIK Uh May, Mexico
@roth.azulik @byroth_ 
📽 Shot by: @loganstrongarms @cshep @reme_martyr 
🧘🏽‍♀️ @lizzymcole @travelwithadrien @reepetite @emchenyoga @zoejanemitchell @tomjauncey @julianmjung @racheltudoryoga 
🎶 No More - lwfi

node.text:
Waterfront brunch goals with @admbrs at The Stay Bosphorus. 🕌 💦 Get exclusive access to the picture-perfect view of the ancient Ortaköy Mosque when you book a stay at this luxury retreat in Istanbul. 🇹🇷

Bask in the opulence of living in a historic mansion overlooking the glistening waters of Bosphorus and the iconic 15 July Martyrs Bridge which connects Europe and Asia. 🌉

Would you stay here when you visit Turkey? Make sure to save this post for your next travel!

📸 @admbrs
📍 @thestaybosphorus, Istanbul, Turkey

Savoring these tranquil moments with @where.to.find.me at the Les Rosees. 🍃 Are you also a fan of these quaint guesthouse stays? 🏠 

This 400-year-old bastide is in the medieval village of Mougins and was carefully renovated to the beauty that it is today using ancient restoration techniques. ⚒️ Each room was designed with different travelers in mind so you will always feel that homey vibe that these small guesthouses are known for. 👌🏻

What are you waiting for? Come and have a siesta by the pool and chill out under the olive trees for a vacation that you will cherish forever. 💦 

Who are you taking with you to this French hideaway? 🇫🇷 

📽️ @where.to.find.me
📍 @lesroseesmougins, France
🎶 Austin Farwell - New Home

node.text:
Getting our last-minute summer tans ready here at the OKU Hotel. 😎 This stylish retreat highlights the raw beauty of nature through its earthy tones and handmade furniture made from natural materials by skilled artisans. ✨ 

Choose from one of the tasteful suites with unique experiences like the Swim Up Room that has direct access to a secluded pool or the Private Villa where you can arrange an exclusive meal made by your own private chef. 👨🏻‍🍳

💡 BH tip: Looking for that perfect beach spot? Visit the turquoise gems of Cala d’en Serra and Sa Caleta. 💦 

📍 @okuhotels, Illes Balears, Spain

Watching the glorious Tuscan sunset here at Villa Cozzano. 🌅 Who else needs a breather from life lately? 🍃 This expansive 28-hectare property is located between the Tuscany and Umbria borders and is home to six beautiful apartments, a vineyard, and olive groves. 🌿 

Aside from the serene wheat fields that envelope this ancient villa, there are also various picturesque locations within the area that can be your next location for that special occasion. 🎑 

When are you booking that next flight out? Share the things that you miss the most about traveling below! ✈️ 

📍 @villacozzano, Italy
🎶 Amore Mio Aiutami (Main Theme) - Piero Piccioni

Driving up to our forest hideaway at the Lake Hartwell A-frame. 🚘 Imagine starting your mornings with a coffee in hand and staring out into the endless views of the lake as you forget about the worries of yesterday. 😌

Spend a perfect weekend here with friends, or just book the whole place for yourself for that much-needed reset as your recharge for the bright future ahead of you. 🍃 

💡 Insider tip: Coffee lovers will be delighted to know that several coffee-making devices are available for your convenience like a Keurig, a Chemex, and a French press. ☕ 

Planning a trip out of town soon? Will you be checking out Georgia?

📍 @heyframehouse, Georgia, USA

Diving blissfully into paradise with @jeremyaustiin and @missangievilla at the @sixsenses Laamu. 💦 Is the Maldives on your travel bucket list this year? 🇲🇻 

This ‘atoll utopia’ is a proud supporter of various marine conservation initiatives that help maintain the balance between sustainable and luxurious tourism in the area. 🦈 Guests are given the opportunity to also learn about these conservation efforts when you participate in the Sustainability Tour that aims to innovate the way the resort operates with reduced emissions and self-sufficiency in mind. ♻️ 

💡 BH tip: Book the Sunset Laamu Water Villa with Pool for an unobstructed panoramic view of one of the best sunsets that you will ever experience in your lifetime! 

📽️ @jeremyaustiin and @missangievilla
📍 @sixsenses, Laamu
🎶 Masked Wolf - Astronaut In The Ocean

When was your last visit to this tropical paradise? Would you stay here? 🇮🇩

- Look for resident cat, "Lilibet"—the Siberian Forest Cat who is part of the trademark resident kittens of the Oetker Collection properties. 🐈
- Get the ultimate royal treatment with your own dedicated butler service and access to the Michelin-starred Céleste restaurant. ✨

Is the UK on your travel list for the year? Would you stay here? 🇬🇧 

📍 @the_lanesborough, London, United Kingdom

Watching this gorgeous sunset in Mallorca with @voyage_provocateur at the Belmond Hotel La Residencia. 🌅 Enjoy the cool breeze while you sip on the finest wines and indulge yourself in sumptuous tapas that celebrates the rich local produce of the region. 🍷

Looking for a healthy treat? Enjoy a candlelit vegetarian dinner at El Olivo by Executive Chef Guillermo Méndez and sample the unique seasonal menus that are especially made for you. 🌿 

Have you been to Mallorca before? Share your travel tips with us below! 🇪🇸 

📽️ @voyage_provocateur
📍 @belmondlaresidencia, Mallorca, Spain
🎶 Max Richter & Daniel Hope & Konzerthaus Kammerorchester Berlin & André De Ridder - Spring 1

Daydreaming in the Maldives with @momentsofgregory at the Seaside Finolhu. How insane is this beach bubble tent? 🌠 Share a romantic moment under the stars inside the Finolhu Bubble that is located away from the rest of the resort where you can see the cosmical Milky Way in the evening and be greeted by the tranquil sunrise in the morning. 🌌 

💡 BH tip: Guests who are staying for at least three nights in a regular villa can avail this unique experience!

Where are you celebrating your next honeymoon? 💙 

📸 @momentsofgregory
📍 @finolhu_maldives, Maldives

Luxury cabin living with @dirtanglass here at The Appalachian A-Frame. 🏡 There’s definitely no room for cabin fever when you book a stay at this spacious retreat that comfortably sleeps up to eight guests. 🌲 

This homey space combines the comforts of contemporary living and the rustic charms of living in a forest by preserving the original 70’s vibes in its interiors while also adding modern touches like gaming consoles and Smart TVs. 📺 🎮 

💡 BH tip: Good doggos are welcome to stay for a small additional fee! 🐕 

📸 @dirtandglass
📍 @appalachianaframe, North Carolina, USA
